ZH: 回声是声音在反射后产生的回响。
EN: An echo is a sound that is reflected back after bouncing off a surface.
ZH: 大厅里的回声使得每个人的声音听起来都很宏亮。
EN: The echo in the hall made everyone's voice sound very grand.
ZH: 我在山谷中大声呼喊，听到了我的回声。
EN: I shouted loudly in the valley and heard my echo.
ZH: 这个洞穴的内部非常空旷，所以我的声音产生了回声。
EN: The interior of this cave is very spacious, so my voice generated an echo.
ZH: 他在峡谷中放了一个小石子，听到了它的回声。
EN: He dropped a small stone in the canyon and heard its echo.
ZH: 她喜欢在山坡上唱歌，因为那里的回声会让她感觉很有力量。
EN: She enjoys singing on the hillside because the echo there makes her feel powerful.
ZH: 大声喊叫可以使得你的声音变得更加响亮，因为它会产生回声。
EN: Shouting loudly can make your voice louder because it creates an echo.
ZH: 我从高楼上向下吹口哨，听到了口哨声的回声。
EN: I whistled from the top of the building and heard the echo of the whistle.
ZH: 将手放在嘴边说话会使声音变得模糊，因为它会导致回声。
EN: Speaking with your hand by your mouth makes your voice unclear because it causes an echo.
ZH: 我们往深井里扔了石头，等了一会儿才听到它们的回声。
EN: We threw stones into the deep well and waited for a while before hearing their echo.
ZH: 空旷的环境能够产生更强烈的回声效果。
EN: An open space can create a more intense echo effect.
ZH: 他敲击大石头听到了石头回声的震撼声音。
EN: He tapped the big rock and heard the stunning sound of the rock's echo.
ZH: 音乐厅用特殊的设计来减少回声，以确保音质的清晰度。
EN: Concert halls use special designs to reduce echo and ensure sound quality clarity.
ZH: 雨后的森林中弥漫着古老的回声，仿佛在诉说着往昔的故事。
EN: The forest after rain is filled with ancient echoes, as if telling tales from the past.
ZH: 她唱歌的声音如此美妙，回声在大厅中持续盘旋。
EN: Her singing voice is so beautiful, the echo continued to linger in the hall.
ZH: 在室内说话时要小声一些，否则会引起回声。
EN: Speak softly indoors, otherwise it will cause an echo.
ZH: 他们站在峭壁上高呼，听到了他们的回声。
EN: They stood on the cliff and shouted loudly, hearing their own echo.
ZH: 回声反应的延迟时间提供了测量声音传播速度的方法。
EN: The delay in the echo provides a method for measuring the speed of sound propagation.
ZH: 在没有回声的地方，声音似乎被吞噬了。
EN: In places without echo, the sound seems to be swallowed up.
ZH: 当我们走进山洞时，我们听到了脚步声的回声。
EN: When we entered the cave, we heard the echo of footsteps.
ZH: 那个地下室很宽敞，我的声音产生了回声。
EN: The basement was spacious, and my voice produced an echo.
ZH: 在寂静的森林中，听到一声尖叫引发了某种回声。
EN: In the silent forest, hearing a scream triggered some sort of echo.
